{"tid":141761,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩freeware加字幕最好","createTime":"2017-03-03T07:29:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-04T06:56:18.000Z","uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4d3a554e139070e40e4532ae4e9818e5546328a0","tid":141761,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:29:56.000Z","msg":"有咩freeware, 可以將srt字幕file同影片檔合併, 而且可以改字體顏色同大細<br />\n咁簡單同常用既function應該無理由冇freeware <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ccf058298ee2241683c5382645c61a2ea1329f1","tid":141761,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9558adbc88f787a8bcce04ca7a8089b50671dd60","tid":141761,"uid":55950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:41:45.000Z","msg":"字幕用 SrtEdit<br />\n合併用 MKVtoolnix<br />\n<br />\n一個做晒好似冇。"},{"pid":"81ee79219372d2d7c53da60a51cc2aeea8307a49","tid":141761,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"ffmpeg"},{"pid":"30e04996f95caa06ae7c7cb8a1e2bcd5e22abc0d","tid":141761,"uid":48491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ffmpeg</blockquote><br />\nffmpeg可以改字幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e4d2b0b5a698d795f5eae8b1b3c7fbf7f5cda0c","tid":141761,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>ffmpeg</blockquote><br />\nffmpeg可以改字幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話合併同埋改字體大小顏色咋嘛<br />\nffmpeg -i input -vf &quot;subtitles='input.srt:force_style='FontName=use what font,Fontsize=u need wt size,PrimaryColour=&amp;Hrgbcolor&amp;'&quot; -c copy output<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3561a59560205512348f009746ec3baebffef144","tid":141761,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T15:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>ffmpeg</blockquote><br />\nffmpeg可以改字幕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話合併同埋改字體大小顏色咋嘛<br />\nffmpeg -i input -vf &quot;subtitles='input.srt:force_style='FontName=use what font,Fontsize=u need wt size,PrimaryColour=&amp;Hrgbcolor&amp;'&quot; -c copy output<br />\n<br />\n好似係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n改字幕係編輯個 srt 檔<br />\nsrt 只係 text file<br />\nsrt 係冇 style 既字幕格式<br />\n要 styled 字幕就要用 ssa / ass<br />\naegisub 係 open source 字幕編輯器<br />\nffmpeg 可以合併 movie file 同 subtitle file<br />\n轉成支援多重字幕軌道既 mkv"},{"pid":"f40d8077dfa85fd212cda724e30ae3b5ff2837c2","tid":141761,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>字幕用 SrtEdit<br />\n合併用 MKVtoolnix<br />\n<br />\n一個做晒好似冇。</blockquote><br />\nAegisub&gt;Srtedit"},{"pid":"22c2bda8f775339a2eefb1994cb6d9eacd4a942c","tid":141761,"uid":14889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"arctime"}]}